“Pokémon 25: The Blue EP” 🤝 Our weekend playlist

“The Blue EP” is out today featuring anthemic remixes by @zhu of “The Red EP” tracks from @mabel, @vincestaples and @cynthialovely! 💙

🔗 Click the link in our bio to listen!

It's said that Piplup can be difficult to bond with...but we have a feeling that won't be a problem with this Piplup! 🥺🐧❤️

This jumbo plush Piplup is now available to preorder at the #PokemonCenter! Tap the link in our bio, US and Canadian Trainers.
